    "title": "Normalized Difference Snow Index (NDSI)",
    "description": "Detects snow from Sentinel-2 L2A imagery using the Normalized Difference Snow Index (NDSI), computed from green and short-wave infrared (SWIR) reflectance. Pixels above a configurable NDSI threshold are classified as snow and rendered in blue; remaining pixels keep a brightened true-color appearance. Converted from the Sentinel Hub NDSI evalscript. Adapted from a SentinelHub Custom Script by Authors not listed.",
